title: GOP-led House report finds no Russia collusion
text:
GOP-led House report finds no Russia collusion 2:28pm EDT - 01:20
The U.S. House Intelligence Committee report, released after the Republican majority voted along party lines to end the probe, found no evidence that President Donald Trump’s pre-campaign business dealings formed a basis for collusion with Russia during the campaign.
